      • BIRTHDAY

        static final java.lang.String BIRTHDAY
        Customer's date of birth. Mandatory for Klarna in Germany, Netherlands and Austria.

        In CTP project the value is type of Date and must be in LocalDate.parse(CharSequence) parsable format, like YYYY-MM-DD.

        Note: Payone API requires birthday as a string in YYYYMMDD format.

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
